<TITLE> Chapai Nawabganj municipal chairman faces extortion case </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Chapai Nawabganj, June 15 (bdnews24.com) A case was filed against Shamim Kabir Helim, chairman of Shibganj municipality and general secretary of municipal BNP Thursday accusing him of cheating on people and extortion, police said. Mominul Haque, a businessman of Daipukuria under the upazila filed the case with Shibganj police station. Lenin Alamgir, the local police chief told bdnews24.com the case was filed at about 9:30 pm. According to the case details Helim took Tk 28 lakh on different occasions by cheating on the plaintiff and also extorted Tk seven lakh from him. Joint forces arrested Shamim Kabir Wednesday night on charges of corruption and irregularities. bdnew
